*     word1.sno - Extract noun phrases matching "the X of Y" or "the X a Y".
*     Tests: ARB as output-capturing side effect in pattern, unanchored scan,
*            alternation (|), looping match on single line.

      PAT      =  " the " ARB . OUTPUT (" of " | " a ")
LOOP  LINE     =  INPUT                            :F(END)
      LINE     ?  PAT                              :(LOOP)
END
